data.description: Nestled on a stunning corner lot, this spacious 4-bedroom, bi-level residence offers an abundance of room to unwind. The first floor welcomes you with custom wood handrails in the foyer, custom cabinetry in the kitchen, (kitchen appliance remain), open living room, formal dining room, bath with double bowl vanity and three inviting bedrooms. Even more space in the lower level,  a family room featuring built-in elements and a brick wood-burning fireplace, full bath, a fourth bedroom, and a convenient laundry area. Outside, as the autumn season paints the landscape with warm colors, you can relish these delightful evenings on the deck or within the confines of the privacy-fenced backyard.
